sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor NV as Nhan vien
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Order as Order Service
    participant Product as Product Service
    participant OrderDB as Order DB
    participant Payment as Payment Service
    participant MQ as RabbitMQ

    NV->>GW: POST /api/orders
    Note over NV,GW: orderChannel=IN_STORE, paymentMethod=CASH<br/>items - productId, quantity, size, toppings<br/>customerId tuy chon, note, discounts
    GW->>Order: Forward request - yeu cau auth STAFF

    loop Moi san pham trong don
        Order->>Product: GET /api/products/:productId
        alt San pham khong hop le
            Product-->>Order: 404 hoac status != ACTIVE
            Order-->>GW: 400 Bad Request
            GW-->>NV: San pham khong ton tai hoac khong kha dung
        else San pham hop le
            Product-->>Order: productName, price
        end
    end

    Order->>Order: buildOrderDetails - tinh subtotal, discount
    Note over Order: initialStatus=CONFIRMED<br/>orderChannel=IN_STORE, paymentMethod=CASH

    Order->>OrderDB: order.create - status=CONFIRMED
    Note over Order,OrderDB: order_details, order_discounts<br/>status_log - changed_by=staffId
    OrderDB-->>Order: order record

    Order->>Payment: POST /api/payments/initiate
    Note over Order,Payment: orderId, totalAmount<br/>paymentMethod=CASH, orderCode

    Payment->>Payment: payment.create - status=PENDING
    Note over Payment: CASH khong can goi API ngoai<br/>cho NV xac nhan sau

    alt HTTP that bai
        Payment-->>Order: 500 Error
        Order->>MQ: Publish order_exchange / order.created
        Note over Order,MQ: Fallback - Payment Service tu tao CASH payment
    else HTTP thanh cong
        Payment-->>Order: 200 OK - paymentId
    end

    Order-->>GW: 201 Created
    Note over Order,GW: orderId, orderCode<br/>status=CONFIRMED, paymentMethod=CASH
    GW-->>NV: Don hang da tao - cho xac nhan thanh toan

    Note over NV,MQ: NV thu tien mat va xac nhan<br/>xem diagram 14

